{"id":232632890,"title":"#推薦 美國品牌-男用香氛","content":"之前逛信義att逛到這間\n維多利亞秘密 的副牌 Bath and body works\n本來以為美國才有\n身為腦粉的我\n沒想到台灣有進\n大買自己的以外還買了男友的\n看到板上很多人討論男香\n推薦給大家😍😍\n\n香水止汗噴霧（左）二合一沐浴洗髮乳（右）\n覺得cp值很高\n香味很夠又可以有止汗效果\n而且運動完還是有香味 直接香一整天\nhttps://i.imgur.com/6GoLTHc.jpg\n二合一那個\n男友已經用到第三瓶了\n男生就是方便就好不用分太多瓶\n出門帶也很方便\n三罐比起來我最愛最右的Noir\n店員說是麝香\n但男友最喜歡中間那個海洋的\n（我聞起來喜歡應該比他自己喜歡重要？😂）\nhttps://i.imgur.com/yf6Yp1g.jpg\n最後附上我回購很多瓶的插電擴香\n這個味道就超多\n之前買金銀花的比較女生\n現在買小清新 比較清爽的香味\n都很喜歡！！！！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/p59v4KW.jpg\n聖誕節快到了送男友禮物的好選擇😍","excerpt":"之前逛信義att逛到這間，維多利亞秘密 的副牌 Bath and body works，本來以為美國才有，身為腦粉的我，沒想到台灣有進，大買自己的以外還買了男友的，看到板上很多人討論男香，推薦給大家，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"1a14ba93-3989-47e5-aedc-a3918963100e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-05T16:22:47.044Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-05T16:22:47.044Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":26,"tags":[],"topics":["男用","香氛","香水","香氛板","男士香水"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"香氛","forumAlias":"fragrance","school":"淡江大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":25},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/6GoLTHc.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/yf6Yp1g.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/p59v4KW.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"5146705f-4cf2-4ae2-9523-7fcb907c68d0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/6GoLTHcl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/6GoLTHcl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/6GoLTHcl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-05T16:22:47.044Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-05T16:22:47.044Z"},{"id":"5146705f-4cf2-4ae2-9523-7fcb907c68d0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/6GoLTHc.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/6GoLT